Good To Know before you go
These pro tips will help you get the most out of your Rewards membership!
You’ll earn 10 points for every dollar spent on eligible items (which breaks down to 1 point for every 10¢). Purchases are rounded to the nearest 10¢.
When will my earnings show in my account?
views.signature: [class]android.view.View[resource_id]None[text]When will my earnings show in my account?[enabled,,]

views.text: Points will typically appear within 72 hours after an in-store purchase or after your online order ships or is picked up from a store.
How long do my earnings last?

Points expire if your account is inactive (no transaction activity) for 365 days.
Rewards expire 90 days after you earn them.
What happens if I make a return?
views.signature: [class]android.view.View[resource_id]None[text]What happens if I make a return?[enabled,,]

views.text: If you make a return, we will deduct the points you earned on those items from your account. If this results in a negative balance, future purchases will be credited to that negative balance. Your Tracker will reflect 0 points earned until the negative balance is met. Please contact
for your most up-to-date points total.
